      "text": "……なぁ怜。カウントダウンライブまであと数日だけど\n……そんなに食べて大丈夫か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Rei. The countdown live is just a few days away.\nIs it okay to eat that much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
