      "text": "ライブ当日に、早食いって……\nどうかしてるんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…on the day of the live performance‚ a speed-eating contest…\nAre they out of their minds?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
