      "text": "……心から同感だ。バンプロからは\n大食いで有名な子は出るらしいけど、さすがにな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I totally agree. Apparently‚ there will be an idol from\nVan Pro who is known for her eating abilities‚ but still…",
